  "intent": "Execute a fully automated Swift 2S Turbo DNA Library Kit protocol for NGS library preparation. Begin with enzymatic fragmentation at 32\u00b0C for specified time, followed by 65\u00b0C for 30 minutes. Perform automated ligation with 30\u03bcL master mix at 20\u00b0C for 20 minutes. Execute magnetic bead purification with 48\u03bcL beads, dual 180\u03bcL 80% ethanol washes, and 22\u03bcL TE elution. Add dual indices (automated or manual) and perform PCR amplification with programmable cycles (3-15). Complete with final magnetic bead cleanup using 32.5\u03bcL beads, ethanol washes, and 22\u03bcL TE elution to yield purified NGS libraries.",
